                        <th>Category</th>
                        <th>Details</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="top-left">Action Plan</td>
                        <td>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Identify communities with critical water and sanitation needs.</li>
                                <li>Train locals in plumbing, borehole construction, and sanitation systems.</li>
                                <li>Partner with NGOs and government bodies for funding and expertise.</li>
